<div class="wikitext">
<a name="price"></a>
<h1>price</h1>
<p>
Returns price of a product, identified by its product code, as found in the <span class="fixedwidth"><a href="http://interchange-rtfm.pullingshots.ca/icdocs/config/ProductFiles.html" title="ProductFiles (config)">ProductFiles</a></span> table(s).
</p>
<a name="Summary"></a>
<h2>Summary</h2>

<p>
<ul>
<li><span class="fixedwidth">&#91;price code]</span></li>
</ul>

<br>
